Package: prsperf
Title: Estimate Theoretical Performance Of PRS
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Levin", , "michael.levin@pennmedicine.upenn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9937-9932"))
Description: A set of functions designed to estimate the optimal
    performance of Polygenic Risk Scores based on heritablity and
    population prevalence. The functions are obtained from:
    https://doi.org/10.1186/1471-2164-13-340.
